5|$|At 14:06 two UH-1E Huey {{helicopters}} carrying General Carey and Colonel Gray (commander of Regimental Landing Team 4 (RLT4)) {{landed at}} the DAO Compound. During {{their approach to}} the compound, Carey and Gray got <b>a</b> <b>firsthand</b> view of the PAVN's firepower as they shelled nearby Tan Son Nhut Airport with ground, rocket, and artillery fire. They quickly established an austere command post {{in preparation for the}} arrival of the Marine CH-53s and the ground security force.|$|E
